19 ("Deputy Orrizzi") was leaving his home to work a night shift
20 and driving a marked 2019 Ford Explorer belonging to the Orange
21 County Sheriff's Office when he pulled out onto Red Bug Lake
22 Road into the path of Sean Hurley's motorcycle, striking Sean
23 Hurley in the lower extremity and throwing him into the grassy
24 median, and
